<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7492ed25-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s140412"><num value="140412">§ 140412.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter, the term “State” includes the District of Columbia and the territories and possessions of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7492ed26-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/111/95/s1/a">Pub. L. 111–95, § 1(a)</ref>, <date date="2009-11-06">Nov. 6, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/3003">123 Stat. 3003</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
